Comment: I saw Morning Glory and it's good. I love Rachel McAdams. I do think she was too obsessed with her job and it almost ruined her relationship with Patrick Wilson. I do feel bad for her that she was fired from her old job because she was doing everything to keep her job. But that's how it happens sometimes at jobs. People get laid off or fired when they least expect it because that's what happened to me at my last job. I like Harrison Ford but I didn't like how he was too grumpy because he didn't wanna be at Daybreak show because he thought it was beneath him. He wanted to continue doing the evening news which he liked doing because he liked reporting important news and I don't blame him for not wanting to do Daybreak. I don't understand how come he didn't continue doing evening news. I know Rachel had talked to him about his contract was gonna be expiring soon but so what. If he had continued doing evening news, he probably would've had to take a pay cut but there's nothing wrong with that if he wants to continue doing something he loved.
